Lano Equipment, Inc, is a second-generation, family-owned and operated equipment dealership established by four brothers just out of the military service in 1946.

The firms original location was on First Street in Chaska, MN. In 1978, Lano Equipment, Inc. moved to a new 16,000 square foot, six-acre facility in Shakopee, MN. In 1991, Lano Equipment, Inc expanded into the north metro area with a new 18,000 square foot facility.

As the case with many distributors, Lano Equipment, Inc. had its roots in agriculture, but has since grown into one of the largest light industrial equipment distributorships in the Twin Cities metropolitan area. Gerhard (Hauser), Joe, Dick, and Clarence Lano are the brothers who made up the first generation of the company. Joe Jr., Roger, Gary, Rod, Brad, and Kurt, represent members of the second Lano generation.

Lano Equipment, Inc. currently lists 62 employees on its payroll between three stores. In addition to Bobcat, the firm represents Kubota, Develon, Toro, Sany, Stihl, Felling Trailers, Load Trail, EBY Trailers, and other significant lines of attachments.
Since 1946, Lano Equipment has been providing the best customer service with the most knowledgable sales staff in the Midwest.
Our values define how we serve our customers, work with partners and set expectation for our team.

Were trusted, long-term partners for our industry. We value the needs of our customers and seek to understand their points of view when solving problems. Were gracious and enthusiastic members of our community.
Were responsible for our outcomes. When the need arises, were never afraid to get in the cab and own it. Our team members push hard to make sure we get excellent customer and business results.
There are no shortcuts when building relationships, technology, and a business. We know that the path to success includes challenges  we embrace those challenges and learn from them.
We look for 10X not 10%. We push the status quo of the industry to deliver more value for our customers, investors and team members.

Our team embrace their authentic selves and leverage their unique backgrounds to help all of us achieve greatness. We strive to be the best version of ourselves and we make space for others to do the same.
